\begin{center}
	{\Large{\bf{OBJECTIVES}}}\\
\end{center}

\begin{itemize}
\item The goal of this site is to be an educational resource to help visualise, learn, and develop different algorithms for the travelling salesman problem in a way that's easily accessible
\item As we apply different algorithms, the current best path is saved and used as input to whatever you run next. The order in which you apply different algorithms to the problem is sometimes referred to as the meta-heuristic strategy
\item To understand the basic framework, current applications and future scope of the algorithm
\item Learn to demonstrate the functionality of the sweep algorithm and site design using Java as the core programming language
\end{itemize}
